&lt;html&gt;&lt;body bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;I really like that solution, although I&#39;d pluralize it.&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Its simply a collection of the leap years.&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;On 2010-08-05, at 7:44 AM, Alexander Johannesen &lt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:alexander.johannesen@...&quot;&gt;alexander.johannesen@...&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote type=&quot;cite&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;




